# Redesign Autopilot

<!-- CURRENT_PHASE: 3 -->

When the user says **"Nästa fas"**, read the CURRENT_PHASE comment above, then:

1. Open `FRONTEND-REDESIGN-MASTERPLAN.md` and find the matching phase
2. Implement ALL changes listed for that phase
3. Run lints on every modified file and fix errors
4. Verify the dev server still compiles (check terminal output)
5. Increment CURRENT_PHASE in this file
6. Report what was done and what to check on localhost:3000

When the user says **"Felsök"**:

1. Run lints on all files changed in the current and previous phases
2. Search for hardcoded colors (hex values, Tailwind color classes like sky-*, indigo-*, cyan-*) in changed files
3. Check for TypeScript errors
4. Fix everything found
5. Report fixes

