## Rules

- NEVER change backend logic, API routes, or data flow
- Always use CSS variables / Tailwind tokens — never hardcode colors
- Color palette (brandbook `public/Brandbook Sajtmaskin.docx`): off-white background (#F7F6F3), near-black foreground + CTA (#0F0F0F), sand accent (#E6E1D8), stone surface (#EFEDE7). No navy, no orange, no mascots.
- Minimalist: as few words as possible in all UI text
